License: BSD
Description: Flask-Oauth2
        ==============
        Flask-Oauth2 is an extension for Flask that allows you to interact with Oauth server
        and also helps you creating your own OAuth server.
        
        :copyright: (c) 2014 - 2015 by HaiNT83.
        :license: BSD, see LICENSE for more details
        
        Flask-OAuth2 relies on oauthlib_, flask_oauthlib_
        .. _oauthlib: https://github.com/idan/oauthlib
        .. _flask_oauthlib: https://github.com/lepture/flask-oauthlib
        
        Features
        --------
        - Support for OAuth2 client, resource server
        - Direct integration with Flask
        - Basic support for remote method invocation of RESTful APIs
        - Support OAuth2 provider with Bearer token
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        1. Enter it 'cd flask_oauth2'
        2. Install it and dependencies `python setup.py install`
        
        
